nodes.text: The Executor of the Empire is an interview article with Star Wars actor Kenneth Colley appearing exclusively in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2013. Conducted by Calum Waddell, the interview discusses the impact of Colley's character, Admiral Firmus Piett, in the films Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back and Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi.
